description: There was "no question" that the US would also not make the list, the foreign minister says.
title: Coronavirus: GB 'unlikely' to make Ireland's travel green list
title_page: Coronavirus: GB 'unlikely' to make Ireland's travel green list - BBC News
maintext: "That's really unfortunate because the two countries we would like to be opening up to in terms of international travel are the UK and US, given the integration between our economy and those two countries.
